item.title: CVE-2023-46653|2023-10-25T13:45:54.971Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20lambdatest-automation%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins lambdatest-automation Plugin 1.20.10 and earlier logs LAMBDATEST Credentials access token at the INFO level, potentially resulting in its exposure.

item.title: CVE-2023-46652|2023-10-25T13:45:54.338Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20lambdatest-automation%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins lambdatest-automation Plugin 1.20.9 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of LAMBDATEST credentials stored in Jenkins.
